                            <comment id="53359" author="pjones" created="Tue, 5 Mar 2013 14:20:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Landed for 2.4&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="53162" author="utopiabound" created="Thu, 28 Feb 2013 01:40:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Make tests run only on SLOW=yes&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/5553&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/5553&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="53155" author="utopiabound" created="Wed, 27 Feb 2013 22:58:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Looking at maloo results for this subtest (&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/query%63utf8%61%37E2%379C%3793%38test_set%91test_set_script_id%93%6179cbec9c%453db2%4511e0%4580c0%4552540025f9af%38sub_test%91sub_test_script_id%93%61525ccaee%453e62%4511e1%4587f0%455254004bbbd3%38sub_test%91status%93%61%38sub_test%91query_bugs%93%61%38test_session%91test_host%93%61%38test_session%91test_group%93%61%38test_session%91user_id%93%61%38test_session%91query_date%93%61%38test_session%91query_recent_period%93%612419200%38test_node%91os_type_id%93%61%38test_node%91distribution_type_id%93%61%38test_node%91architecture_type_id%93%61%38test_node%91file_system_type_id%93%6100437f32%45318d%4511e1%459c6d%455254004bbbd3%38test_node%91lustre_branch_id%93%61%38test_node_network%91network_type_id%93%61%38commit%61Update%43results&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;ZFS Results&lt;/a&gt;) the test takes 2600+ seconds.  So most failure seem to be just long running tests, instead of explicit failures.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I propose makeing this test and sanity-quota test 12a run SLOW only for zfs until sync has been sped up.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="53151" author="utopiabound" created="Wed, 27 Feb 2013 21:54:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This may be the same slow sync issue as &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2887&quot; title=&quot;sanity-quota test_12a: slow due to ZFS VMs sharing single disk&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-2887&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-2887&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
